@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jldhid(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.91) / wp.exp(v1 + 0.33)) - wp.abs(v2))
    v0 = ((0.38 * (v0 + 0.36 + v2 + 0.24)) - wp.cos((v0 + 0.08 - tmp + 0.34)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs((v1 + 0.99 * v1 + 0.54)))
    v2 = v2
    v2 = ((v1 - tmp) / wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.77)))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
